cogl: cogl (Rendering Library)
cogl:
cogl: Cogl is a small open source library for using 3D graphics hardware
cogl: for rendering.
cogl:
cogl: The API departs from the flat state machine style of OpenGL and is
cogl: designed to make it easy to write orthogonal components that can
cogl: render without stepping on each others toes.
cogl:
cogl: Project URL: https://github.com/GNOME/cogl/
cogl:
